@startuml
title SongSpiration / MusicPin — Diagram klas (model danych)

' Ustawienia czytelności
hide methods

' Test comment to trigger workflow - update 2
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam linetype ortho

' ===== Enumeracje / typy pomocnicze =====
enum TokenType {
  access
  refresh
}

enum PinVisibility {
  public
  private
  unlisted
}

enum Instrument {
  Guitar
  Bass
  Drums
  Unknown
}

' ===== Encje =====
class User {
  +id: UUID
  +email: string
  +password_hash: string
  +display_name: string
  +avatar_url: string
  +bio: string
  +roles: string
  +created_at: datetime
  +last_login: datetime
  +is_email_verified: bool
}

class AuthToken {
  +id: UUID
  +user_id: UUID
  +token_hash: string
  +type: TokenType
  +expires_at: datetime
  +revoked_at: datetime
  +created_at: datetime
}

class Pin {
  +id: UUID
  +owner_id: UUID
  +title: string
  +description: string
  +instrument: Instrument
  +visibility: PinVisibility

  +gp_file_location_or_blob: string
  +filename: string
  +mime_type: string
  +size: long
  +checksum: string

  +created_at: datetime
  +updated_at: datetime
}

class Genre {
  +id: UUID
  +name: string
  +slug: string
}

class PinGenre {
  +pin_id: UUID
  +genre_id: UUID
}

class Like {
  +user_id: UUID
  +pin_id: UUID
  +created_at: datetime
  ..constraints..
  {unique} (user_id, pin_id)
}

' ===== Relacje =====
User "1" -- "0..*" Pin : owner
User "1" -- "0..*" AuthToken : sessions

Pin "1" -- "0..*" Like
User "1" -- "0..*" Like

Pin "1" -- "0..*" PinGenre
Genre "1" -- "0..*" PinGenre

note right of PinGenre
Tabela łącznikowa many-to-many
Pin ↔ Genre
end note

note right of AuthToken
W specyfikacji: AuthToken/Session
Przechowuje hash tokenu oraz typ
(access/refresh), daty i revokację.
end note

@enduml
